<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٨٩٧ -<span class="c5"> عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ:</span> وقَالَ قَتَادَةُ: فِي بَعْضِ الْحُرُوفِ: <span class="c2">«وَتُسَبِّحُوا اللَّهَ بُكْرَةً وَعَشِيًّا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>